item.title: CVE-2020-25846|2024-09-17T01:41:45.846Z -- changing%20inc. -- nhiservisignadapter
item.description: The digest generation function of NHIServiSignAdapter has not been verified for source file path, which leads to the SMB request being redirected to a malicious host, resulting in the leakage of user's credential.
